quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,51,"(Kananjalo uAllâh Wathi: “Hini na bantu), musani ukuthabatha oothixo ababini. Inene uAllâh nguYe kuphela OnguThixo,yoyikani Mna ke nina ngamandla"
  16,52,KokwaKhe konke okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni neNkolo yokwenene ngonaphakade. Ingaba ke ngoku niya koyika thixo bambi na ngaphandle koAllâh
  16,53,"Kananjalo nantoni na eziintsikelelo nelungileyo eninayo, ivela kuAllâh. Kwaye xa okubi kunichukumisa, nikhala kuYe kakhulu nikhalela uncedo"
  16,54,"Athi Esakubususa ububi obo kuni, khangela ke! Abanye3 benu bayamanise abanye kunqulo lweNkosi yabo (uAllâh)"
  16,55,Ngoko ke bayakuphika oko bakuphiwe siThi. Vuyani ke okwakaloku nje kodwa kungekudala niza kwazi (nizisole)
  16,56,"Kananjalo babalela inxalenye yoko Sibaphe kona kwizinto abangenalwazi ngazo. (Ndifunga) ngoAllâh, niza kubuzwa ngokwenene ngako konke enanikuqamba (emhlabeni)"
  16,57,Kananjalo babalela iintombi4 kuAllâh! Makazukiswe Yena (Uphakamile Ukude le) Ungentla kwazo zonke izinto abazibalela kuYe! Nakoko kunqwenelwa ngabo buqu
  16,58,"Xa iindaba (zokuzalwa) komntwana oyintombazana zisaziswa nawuphi na kubo, ubuso bakhe buyafiphala, izale (intliziyo) yakhe bubuhlungu ngaphakathi kwakhe"
  16,59,Azifihle ebantwini ngenxa yobubi axelelwe ngabo. Uza kumgcina (loo mntwana uyintombazana) elihlazo elinjalo okanye uza kumngcwaba ephila emhlabeni? Inene singcolile isigqibo (abasithabathayo)
  16,60,"(UBomi oBuzayo) kwabo bangakholwayo kuBomi oBuzayo buyinkcazo engcolileyo (kubo). KuAllâh yinkcazo ephakamileyo yaye Yena nguSomandla, uSobulumko"